(3) Create weight difference variables
wd1 = weight0 - weight1;
wd2 = weight0 - weight2;
wd12 = weight1 - weight2;*/

/*check data --- there are other ways checking data, here I am using the Knowledge introduced in this course;
**for continuous numeric vars;*/
